A0the%20ED%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-massive-show-of-unity-at-rally-to-support-arvind-kejriwal-5345521%5C%22%3EINDIA%20Bloc's%20%26quot%3B5%20Demands%26quot%3B%20To%20Election%20Commission%20At%20Mega%20Rally%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20money%20laundering%20charges%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20also%20said%20it%20may%20need%20his%20custody%20again%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20gave%20false%20evidence%20against%20other%20AAP%20members%2C%20and%20when%20confronted%20with%20the%20statements%20of%20his%20own%20party%20leaders%2C%20he%20called%20them%20confused.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20AAP%20communications%20in-charge%20who%20has%20turned%20an%20approver%2C%20didn't%20report%20to%20him%20but%20to%20Atishi%20and%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20lawyer%20has%20demanded%20some%20medicines%20and%20a%20special%20diet%20for%20him%20inside%20the%20jail%20in%20view%20of%20his%20illness.%20A%20request%20has%20also%20been%20made%20to%20provide%20a%20copy%20of%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHow%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%3C%2Fem%3E%20(by%20Neerja%20Chowdhury)%20to%20the%20jailed%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20against%20his%20arrest%2C%20arguing%20that%20his%20fundamental%20rights%20were%20violated%20by%20the%20probe%20agency.%20The%20court%20had%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20seeking%20a%20reply%20by%20April%202.%20The%20hearing%20will%20resume%20on%20April%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20third%20AAP%20leader%20after%20his%20former%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Rajya%2