mmunist%20Party%20of%20India-Marxist%20(CPI-M)%2C%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist%E2%80%93Leninist)%20Liberation%20(CPI-ML)%2C%20saw%20significant%20success%2C%20particularly%20for%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20which%20won%2016%20out%20of%2029%20contested%20seats.%20This%20performance%20gives%20them%20a%20rationale%20to%20vie%20for%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20South%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-2024-congress-dominance-continues-in-thiruvananthapuram-5195323%5C%22%3EINDIA%20bloc%20partners%20in%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20targeting%20two%20crucial%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20traditionally%20held%20by%20the%20Congress.%20Even%20before%20the%20Congress%20renominated%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20CPI%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-congress-said-on-left-fighting-from-rahul-gandhis-constituency-wayanad-5145988%5C%22%3Eannounced%20Annie%20Raja%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20prominent%20leader%20and%20member%20of%20its%20national%20executive%2C%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20constituency.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Left%20alliance%20has%20nominated%20Pannan%20Raveendran%20to%20challenge%20Congress%20candidate%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%2C%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20is%20the%20BJP's%20candidate%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20party%20general%20secretary%20K.C.%20Venugopal%20against%20sitting%20CPI(M)%20parliamentarian%20A.M.%20Arif%20from%20Alappuzha%2C%20aiming%20to%20regain%20lost%20ground%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20as%20the%20electoral%20landscape%20evolves%20and%20alliances%20shift%2C%20the%20dynamics%20of%20friendly%20contests%20and%20strategic%20manoeuvres%20continue%20to%20shape%20the%20political%20landscape%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20too%20many%20occurrences%20of%20friendly%20contests%20across%20states.%20Jharkhand%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20no%20exception.%20Here%2C%20the%20CPI%20has%20severed%20ties%20with%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%2C%20stating%20its%20intention%20to%20contest%20eight%20out%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20Notably%2C%20the%20CPI%20does%20not%20hold%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Contest%20In%20Haryana%2037%20Years%20Ago%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earliest%20instance%20of%20such%20a%20friendly%20contest%20can%20be%20traced%20back%2037%20years%20ago%20in%20Haryana.%20According%20to%20journalist%20and%20author%20Anil%20Maheshwari%2C%20Devi%20Lal%20orchestrated%20an%20alliance%20of%20all%20opposition%20parties%20to%20challenge%20the%20then%20incumbent%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Bansi%20Lal%2C%20allotting%20one%20seat%20each%20to%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20CPI(M)%20out%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lok%20Dal%20of%20Devi%20Lal%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20the%20dominant%20partners.%20It%20was%20for%20the%20first%20and%20the%20last%20time%20that%20the%20communist%20parties%20marked%20their%20presence%20in%20the%20Haryana%20Legislative%20Assembly.%20There%20was%20a%20conflict%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20CPI(M)%20over%20the%20Fatehabad%20seat%20in%20Hissar%2C%20with%20both%20staking%20their%20claim%20to%20it.%20Devi%20Lal%20came%20up%20with%20a%20solution%2C%20and%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20'friendly%20contest'%2C%20asked%20both%20the%20parties%20to%20contest.%20But%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20alliance%20-%20that%20was%20arrived%20at%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20adjustments%20and%20compromises%20-%20to%20fall%20apart%20on%20account%20of%20one%20seat.%20The%20result%20was%20that%20the%20coalition%20bagged%2085%20out%20of%2090%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Power%20of%20the%20Ballot%3A%20Travail%20and%20Triumph%20in%20the%20Elections%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20co-authored%20with%20Vipul%20Maheswari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Balbir%20Singh%20Choudhary%20of%20the%20BJP%20defeated%20Prithvi%20Singh%20Gorkhpuria%20of%20the%20CPI(M)%20by%2028%2C615%20votes%20in%20the%20'friendly%20contest'%20in%201987%20in%20the%20Fatehabad%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimilar%20Equations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20outcome%20not%20only%20marked%20a%20personal%20victory%20for%20Devi%20Lal%20but%20also%20dealt%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi-led%20Congress.%20Subsequently%2C%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20called%20for%20his%20resignation%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20blamed%20the%20party%20apparatus%20for%20the%20defeat.%20This%20discord%20within%20the%20Congress%20led%20to%20calls%20for%20party%20elections%20to%20appoint%20a%20full-time%20president%20dedicated%20solely%20to%20running%20the%20organisation%2C%20without%20the%20added%20responsibility%20of%20leading%20the%20nation%20as%20prime%20minister.%20Meanwhile%2C%20following%20his%20last%20term%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Devi%20Lal%20transitioned%20to%20central%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20players%20may%20have%20changed%2C%20the%20equations%20remain%2C%20and%20countering%20the%20might%20and%20strategy%20of%20today's%20BJP%20may%20prove%20challenging.%20With%20more%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%20contests%26quot%3B%20today%2C%20things%20are%20increasingly%20likely%20to%20favour%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jayanta%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%C2%A0writing%20on%20polls%20and%20politics%2C%20conflict%2C%20farmer%20and%20human%20interest%20issues)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711958460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9attocj_india-bloc_640x480_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%