3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%2C%20however%2C%20had%20admitted%20that%20he%20was%20driving%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20hurry%26quot%3B.%20After%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20many%20on%20social%20media%20criticised%20the%20car%20driver%20for%20%26quot%3Breckless%20driving%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20agreed%20that%20violence%20can't%20be%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711958040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flrs65bqo_bengaluru-road-rage_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-in-focus-as-woman-films-men-tailing-car-punching-doors-5350687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20police%20have%20caught%20three%20men%20after%20a%20video%20of%20them%20tailing%20a%20car%20on%20a%20scooter%2C%20banging%20on%20its%20windows%20and%20trying%20to%20open%20its%20doors%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-in-focus-as-woman-films-men-tailing-car-punching-doors-5350687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-in-focus-as-woman-films-men-tailing-car-punching-doors-5350687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-in-focus-as-woman-films-men-tailing-car-punching-doors-5350687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20New%20Change%20In%20Tax%20Regime%26quot%3B%3A%20Government%20Explains%20What%20Changes%20From%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20on%20Sunday%20clarified%20that%20there%20is%20no%20new%20change%20in%20the%20tax%20regime%20that%20is%20coming%20into%20effect%20from%20April%201.%20Just%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20interim%20budget's%20income%20tax%20proposals%20coming%20into%20effect%2C%20the%20finance%20ministry%20debunked%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20concerning%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20clearing%20the%20confusion%20over%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%20In%20a%20detailed%20note%2C%20the%20ministry%20explained%20that%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20has%20low%20rates%20but%20fewer%20exemptions%20and%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20come%20to%20notice%20that%20misleading%20information%20related%20to%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20is%20being%20spread%20on%20some%20social%20media%20platforms.%20It%20is%20therefore%20clarified%20that%3A%20There%20is%20no%20new%20change%20which%20is%20coming%20in%20from%2001.04.2024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20shared%20a%20table%20explaining%20the%20income%20tax%20slabs%20as%20per%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%20It%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20tax%20regime%20under%20section%20115BAC(1A)%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Finance%20Act%202023%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20existing%20old%20regime%20(without%20exemptions)%20(SEE%20TABLE%20BELOW)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B90%20to%20%E2%82%B93%2C00%2C000%3A%200%20per%20cent%20tax%20rate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B93%2C00%2C001%20to%20%E2%82%B96%2C00%2C000%3A%205%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B96%2C00%2C001%20to%20%E2%82%B99%2C00%2C000%3A%2010%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B99%2C00%2C001%20to%20%E2%82%B912%2C00%2C000%3A%2015%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B912%2C00%2C001%20to%20%E2%82%B915%2C00%2C001%3A%2020%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20above%20%E2%82%B915%2C00%2C000%3A%2030%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20old%20tax%20regime%2C%20the%20income%20tax%20slabs%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B90%20to%20%E2%82%B92.5lakh%3A%200%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B9%202.5%20-%20%E2%82%B9%205lakh%3A%205%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20from%20%E2%82%B9%205-%20%E2%82%B910%20lakh%3A%2020%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncome%20above%20%E2%82%B9%2010%20lakh%3A%2030%20per%20cent%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CNew%20tax%20regime%20is%20applicable%20for%20persons%20other%20than%20companies%20and%20firms%2C%20is%20applicable%20as%20a%20default%20regime%20from%20the%20Financial%20Year%202023-24%20and%20the%20Assessment%20Year%20corresponding%20to%20this%20is%20AY%202024-25.%20Under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20the%20tax%20rates%20are%20significantly%20lower%2C%20though%20the%20benefit%20of%20various%20exemptions%20and%20deductions%20(other%20than%20the%20standard%20deduction%20of%20Rs.%2050%2C000%20from%20salary%20and%20Rs.%2015%2C000%20from%20the%20family%20pension)%20is%20not%20available%2C%20as%20in%20the%20old%20regime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CNew%20tax%20regime%20is%20the%20default%20tax%20regime%2C%20however%2C%20taxpayers%20can%20choose%20the%20tax%20regime%20(old%20or%20new)%20that%20they%20think%20is%20beneficial%20to%20them.%20Option%20for%20opting%20out%20from%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20is%20available%20till%20filing%20of%20return%20for%20the%20AY%202024-25.%20Eligible%20persons%20without%20any%20business%20income%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20the%20regime%20for%20each%20financial%20year.%20So%2C%20they%20can%20choose%20a%20new%20tax%20regime%20in%20one%20financial%20year%20and%20an%20old%20tax%20regime%20in%20another%20year%20and%20vice%20versa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20has%20come%20to%20notice%20that%20misleading%20information%20related%20to%20new%20tax%20regime%20is%20being%20spread%20on%20some%20social%20media%20platforms.