tax%20regime%20has%20low%20rates%20but%20fewer%20exemptions%20and%20deductions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-fresh-change-in-new-tax-regime-finance-ministrys-fact-check-on-claims-5349572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNehru%20Saw%20It%20As%20Nuisance%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20Doubles%20Down%20On%20Katchatheevu%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20charge%20at%20Opposition%20over%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20row%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20said%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20wanted%20to%20give%20away%20the%20island%20to%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201974%2C%20the%20then%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20had%20accepted%20the%20uninhabited%20island%2C%20about%201.6%20km%20long%20and%20over%20300%20m%20wide%2C%20a%20Sri%20Lankan%20area%20under%20Indo-Sri%20Lankan%20maritime%20agreement.%20The%20issue%20has%20resurfaced%20after%20a%20media%20report%20based%20on%20a%20RTI%20reply%20received%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20on%20the%201974%20pact.%20In%201976%2C%20after%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20was%20dismissed%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20another%20pact%20restricted%20fishermen%20of%20both%20countries%20from%20fishing%20in%20each%20other's%20waters.%20The%20harassment%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20fishermen%20by%20Lankan%20authorities%20is%20a%20key%20issue%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20raised%20this%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Mr%20Annamalai%20nor%20the%20newspaper%20have%20shared%20the%20RTI%20reply%2C%20and%20NDTV%20can't%20independently%20verify%20the%20content%20and%20the%20date%20it%20was%20issued%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20AIADMK%20chief%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Jayalalithaa%20had%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20Congress%20on%20this%20issue%20and%20had%20demanded%20a%20lease%20in%20perpetuity%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20granting%20fishing%20rights%20to%20Indian%20fishermen%20in%20Lankan%20waters.%20She%20had%20also%20pressed%20for%20steps%20to%20retrieve%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20today%20quoted%20former%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Swaran%20Singh's%201974%20address%20in%20Parliament.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20confident%20that%20the%20agreement%20demarcating%20the%20maritime%20boundary%20in%20the%20Palk%20Bay%20will%20be%20considered%20as%20fair%2C%20just%20and%20equitable%20to%20both%20countries.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20remind%20the%20honourable%20members%20that%20in%20concluding%20this%20agreement%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20fishing%2C%20pilgrimage%20and%20navigation%2C%20which%20both%20sides%20have%20enjoyed%20in%20the%20past%2C%20have%20been%20fully%20safeguarded%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20former%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20two%20years%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20there%20was%20another%20agreement%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20agreement%2C%20India%20proposed%20the%20following%3A%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20exclusive%20economic%20zones%20by%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20exercise%20sovereign%20rights%20over%20the%20living%20and%20non-living%20resources%20of%20their%20respective%20zones.%20The%20fishing%20vessels%20and%20fishermen%20of%20India%20shall%20not%20engage%20in%20fishing%20in%20the%20historic%20waters%2C%20the%20territorial%20sea%20and%20the%20exclusive%20zone%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(In)%201974%2C%20assurance%20is%20given.%20By%201976%2C%20an%20agreement%20is%20concluded%20which%20gives%20away%20this%20assurance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consequence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%206%2C184%20Indian%20fishermen%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20In%20the%20same%20period%2C%201%2C175%20Indian%20fishing%20vessels%20have%20been%20seized%20by%20Lankans%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Katchatheevu%20issue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20raised%20in%20Parliament%20by%20various%20parties%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20written%20to%20me%20numerous%20times.%20My%20record%20shows%20that%20I%20have%20replied%20to%20the%20current%20Chief%20Minister%20(MK%20Stalin)%2021%20times%20on%20this%20issue.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20which%20has%20suddenly%20surfaced.%20This%20is%20a%20live%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20DMK%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20approached%20the%20matter%20%26quot%3Bas%20though%20they%20have%20no%20responsibility%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20the%20public%20has%20a%20right%20to%20know%20how%20this%20situation%20came%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20who%20did%20this%2C%20how%20the%20situation%20arose.%20What%20we%20do%20not%20know%20is%20who%20hid%20this%2C%20what%20has%20been%20concealed%20from%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20claim%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20mainly%20that%20the%20Kathatheevu%20island%20belonged%20to%20the%20Raja%20of%20Ramnad%20and%20that%20he%20had%20it%20from%20the%20British%20era.%20Later%20on%2C%20his%20rights%20moved%20to%20the%20Madras%20government.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20view%20was%20also%20that%20there%20was%20no%20documentary%20evidence%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20had%20an%20original%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20argument%20was%20that%20they%20have%20records%20going%20back%20to%20the%2017th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20both%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20became%20independent%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20were%20issues%20between%20these%20countries%20about%20using%20this%20island.%20In%201974%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%2C%20said%20then%20Sri%20Lankan%20Prime%20Minister%20Sirimavo%20Bandaranaike%20and%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20spoke%20about%20this%20on%20the%20latter's%20trip%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201958%2C%20then%20Attorney%20General%20MC%20Setalvad%20said%20in%20a%20legal%20opinion%20that%20while%20the%20matter%20is%20not%20free%20from%20difficulty%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20balance%20lies%20in%20favour%20of%20concluding%20that%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20island%20was%20and%20is%20in%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20people%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20a%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20felt%20that%20we%20must%20at%20least%20insist%20for%20fishing%20rights%20around%20the%20island.%20%26quot%3BThe%20island%20was%20also%20given%20away%20in%201974%20and%20the%20fishing%20rights%20in%201976%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20did%20this%20happen%20has%20many%20aspects%20to%20it.%20One%20is%20the%20indifference%20shown%20by%20the%20central%20government%20and%20Prime%20Ministers%20of%20the%20day%20about%20the%20territory%20of%20India.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20they%20simply%20did%20not%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20an%20observation%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru%20in%20May%201961%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20attach%20no%20importance%20at%20all%20to%20this%20little%20island%20and%20I%20would%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20giving%20up%20our%20claim%20to%20it.%20I%20do%20not%20like%20matters%20like%20this%20pending%20indefinitely%20and%20being%20raised%20again%20and%20again%20in%20Parliament.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20to%20Pandit%20Nehru%2C%20this%20was%20a%20little%20island%2C%20he%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20nuisance.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20sooner%20you%20give%20it%20away%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20view%2C%20he%20said%2C%20continued%20in%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20era.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20remarked%20in%20a%20Congress%20meeting%20that%20this%20island%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20rock%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20dismissive%20attitude%20was%20the%20historic%20Congress%20attitude%20towards%20Katchatheevu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister's%20press%20interaction%20came%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20for%20%26quot%3Bcallously%26quot%3B%20giving%20away%20the%20island%20to%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEye-opening%20and%20startling!%20New%20facts%20reveal%20how%20Congress%20callously%20gave%20away%20Katchatheevu.%20This%20has%20angered%20every%20Indian%20and%20reaffirmed%20in%20people's%20minds%20-%20we%20can't%20ever%20trust%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X%2C%20sharing%20the%20report.%26quot%3B%20Sharing%20a%20media%20report%20that%20said%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20taken%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20Karunanidhi%20into%20confidence%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20island%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20DMK%20has%20%26quot%3Bdone%20nothing%26quot%3B%20to%20safeguard%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Manickam%20Tagore%20hit%20back%2C%20calling%20the%20BJP's%20charge%20on%20the%20issue%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiversionary%20tactic%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20BJP%2C%20RSS%20and%20PM%20Modi%20is%20that%20people%20are%20rejecting%20them%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20they%20want%20a%20diversionary%20tactic...%20The%20government%20of%20India%20headed%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20signed%20an%20agreement%20called%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi-Sirimavo%20Bandaranaike%20agreement%20in%20that%20time%20to%20save%206%20lakh%20Tamils%20and%20to%20save%20them%2C%20this%20island%20was%20given%20to%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government.%20We%20are%20very%20clear%20that%20if%20our%20fishermen%20are%20attacked%2C%20we%20will%20raise%20our%20voices%20to%20take%20back%20Katchatheevu%20Island.%20But%2C%20in%2010%20years%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20They%20will%20not%20get%20even%20one%20seat%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20by%20these%20cheap%20tactics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK's%20A%20Saravanan%20said%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20has%20said%20nothing%20new.%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20raking%20up%20this%20issue%20now.%20Because%20they%20are%20scared%2C%20they%20know%20they%20are%20going%20to%20lose%20this%20election%20and%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20they%20are%20facing%20a%20rout.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20cannot%20answer%20the%20question%2C%20why%20no%20flood%20relief%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20He%20is%20now%20bringing%20up%20false%20bogeys%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711958040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fsmblpqcg_s-jaishankar_650x400_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-nehru-wanted-to-give-it-away-s-jaishankar-as-katchatheevu-row-heats-up-5349465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doubling%20down%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20charge%20at%20Opposition%20over%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20row%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20said%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20wanted%20to%20give%20away%20the%20island%20to%20Lanka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-nehru-wanted-to-give-it-away-s-jaishankar-as-katchatheevu-row-heats-up-5349465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Min%20Kyu%20enlists%20for%20military%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publis