B%22title%22%3A%22Anupam%20Mittal%20talks%20about%20spending%20a%20%2425%2C000%20on%20brand's%20domain%20name%20in%20the%201990s%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711955664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108936591%2Cimgsize-572658.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fshark-tank-india-3s-anupam-mittal-talks-about-spending-a-whopping-25000-on-his-brands-domain-name-in-the-1990s-says-we-had-saved-about-30000-in-our-company%2Farticleshow%2F108936604.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anupam%20Mittal%20invested%20%2425%2C000%20from%20%2430%2C000%20savings%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20for%20a%20domain%2C%20crucial%20for%20their%20IT%20solutions%20company.%20He%20discussed%20challenges%20in%20the%20Indian%20dating%20app%20sector%2C%20popular%20among%20the%20younger%20generation.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20Anupam%20had%20to%20say%20on%20spending%20more%20than%20half%20of%20his%20savings%20on%20his%20domain%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20To%20Lose%20Seat%2C%20His%20Party%20To%20Hit%20Record%20Low%20In%20UK%20Polls%3A%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20so-called%20mega%20poll%20released%20by%20a%20civil%20society%20campaign%20organisation%20indicates%20that%20the%20governing%20Conservative%20Party%20is%20in%20for%20a%20major%20drubbing%20in%20the%20general%20election%20expected%20later%20this%20year%2C%20with%20even%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20seat%20in%20North%20Yorkshire%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2015%2C029-person%20MRP%20poll%20conducted%20by%20Survation%20on%20behalf%20of%20Best%20for%20Britain%20puts%20the%20Opposition%20Labour%20Party%20on%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20with%20a%2019-point%20lead%20over%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20up%20three%20points%20from%20the%20group's%20previous%20poll%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year.%20%E2%80%98The%20Sunday%20Times'%20analysis%20of%20the%20major%20seat-by-seat%20survey%20claims%20Tory%20prospects%20have%20hit%20a%20record%20low%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20on%20track%20for%20their%20worst%20election%20result%2C%20winning%20fewer%20than%20100%20seats.%20Labour%20could%20win%20468%2C%20giving%20Opposition%20leader%20Sir%20Keir%20Starmer's%20party%20a%20whopping%20286-seat%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20MRP%20forecast%20shows%20that%2C%20if%20the%20election%20were%20held%20tomorrow%2C%20Sunak's%20Conservatives%20would%20lose%20250%20MPs%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20Labour%20Party%20would%20win%20with%20468%20seats.%20This%20would%20be%20the%20worst%20ever%20result%20for%20the%20Conservatives%20at%20a%20General%20Election%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20the%20Best%20for%20Britain%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20extent%20of%20the%20damage%20to%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20doesn't%20stop%20there%20either.%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20seat%20of%20Richmond%20and%20Northallerton%20becomes%20a%20hyper-marginal%2C%20with%20the%20Labour%20Party%20just%202.4%20per%20cent%20behind%20him.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20in%20Chancellor%20Jeremy%20Hunt's%20new%20seat%20of%20Godalming%20and%20Ash%20in%20which%20the%20Liberal%20Democrats%20trail%20by%20just%201%20per%20cent%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20claims%20that%20of%20the%20estimated%2028%20sitting%20Cabinet%20members%20expected%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%2C%20only%2013%20of%20them%20would%20be%20re-elected%20should%20they%20decide%20to%20stand%20again.%20While%20undecided%20voters%20were%20not%20accounted%20for%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20they%20represented%20about%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20those%20asked%20and%20the%20Tories%20will%20be%20pinning%20their%20hopes%20on%20winning%20them%20over%20when%20the%20country%20finally%20goes%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELord%20David%20Frost%2C%20the%20former%20Brexit%20secretary%20and%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20Sunak%2C%20told%20'The%20Sunday%20Times'%20that%20these%20latest%20survey%20figures%20showed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdesperate%20situation%E2%80%9D%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20was%20facing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20polling%20is%20getting%20worse%20over%20time%2C%20not%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak's%20aides%20fear%20he%20could%20face%20a%20leadership%20challenge%20after%20the%20local%20elections%20if%2C%20as%20predicted%2C%20the%20Tories%20face%20humiliating%20defeats%20in%20the%20May%202%20local%20council%20and%20mayoral%20polls.%20It%20will%20revive%20talk%20of%20rebellion%20in%20his%20party%20ranks%2C%20which%20have%20never%20fully%20quietened%20down%20with%20Tory%20MPs%20fearful%20of%20losing%20their%20seats%20when%20the%20general%20election%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Sunak%20tried%20to%20call%20an%20election%2C%20I%20think%20there%20would%20be%20a%20real%20risk%20of%20an%20unedifying%20situation%20when%20a%20serious%20attempt%20would%20have%20been%20made%20to%20remove%20the%20PM%20before%20the%20final%20dissolution%20of%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20Tory%20MP%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20certainly%20several%20MPs%20who%20said%20they%20would%20have%20immediately%20put%20letters%20in%20to%20force%20a%20confidence%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2053%20MPs%20would%20need%20to%20sign%20letters%20of%20no-confidence%20for%20the%20party's%20powerful%20backbench%201922%20Committee%20to%20force%20such%20a%20vote%20of%20no-confidence%20in%20Sunak.%20Rebels%20claim%20they%20are%20in%20the%20mid-20s%20now%2C%20with%20at%20least%20another%2010%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20ranks%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repeal%20of%20the%20Fixed-term%20Parliaments%20Act%20in%202022%20restored%20the%20ability%20of%20British%20prime%20ministers%20to%20set%20election%20dates.%20However%2C%20by%20law%20a%20general%20election%20has%20to%20take%20place%20at%20least%20every%20five%20years%2C%20making%20January%202025%20the%20outermost%20deadline%20for%20Sunak%20to%20go%20to%20the%20ballot%20box.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20indicated%20that%20he%20intends%20to%20call%20a%20general%20election%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202024%2C%20with%20October-November%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20possible%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711955400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6om28o0g_rishi-sunak-reuters_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-to-lose-seat-his-party-to-hit-record-low-in-uk-polls-survey-5345469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20so-called%20mega%20poll%20released%20by%20a%20civil%20society%20campaign%20organisation%20indicates%20that%20the%20governing%20Conservative%20Party%20is%20in%20for%20a%20major%20drubbing%20in%20the%20election%20expected%20later%20this%20year%2C%20with%20even%20UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20seat%20hanging%20in%20balance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-to-lose-seat-his-party-to-hit-record-low-in-uk-polls-survey-5345469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-to-lose-seat-his-party-to-hit-record-low-in-uk-polls-survey-5345469%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-to-lose-seat-his-party-to-hit-record-low-in-uk-polls-survey-5345469%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Iranian%20prisoner%20to%20run%20London%20Marathon%22