ID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftech-investor-buys-crypt-next-to-marilyn-monroe-and-hugh-hefner-13105850%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20burial%20crypt%20next%20to%20the%20resting%20place%20of%20Marilyn%20Monroe%20and%20Playboy%20founder%20Hugh%20Hefner%20has%20been%20bought%20by%20a%20tech%20investor%20for%20%C2%A3154%2C000%20(%24195%2C000).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftech-investor-buys-crypt-next-to-marilyn-monroe-and-hugh-hefner-13105850%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Coercive%20Steps%20Over%20Rs%203%2C500%20Crore%20Demand%26quot%3B%3A%20Tax%20Relief%20For%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20relief%20to%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Centre%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20that%20it%20will%20not%20act%20against%20the%20Opposition%20party%20to%20recover%20tax%20dues%20amounting%20to%20over%20Rs%203%2C500%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20July%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20it%20received%20notices%20from%20Income%20Tax%20department%2C%20seeking%20payment%20of%20tax%20dues%20amounting%20to%20a%20whopping%20Rs%203%2C567%20crore.%20The%20Opposition%20party%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Btax%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20and%20alleged%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department's%20move%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20choke%20it%20financially%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20polls.%20The%20party%20has%20said%20this%20was%20disrupting%20the%20level-playing%20field%20for%20the%20polls%20and%20also%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20tax%20authorities%20withdrew%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%20135%20crore%20from%20a%20party's%20accounts%20for%20dues%20from%20previous%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20case%20came%20up%20before%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20today%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20the%20central%20agency%20will%20take%20no%20coercive%20action%20against%20the%20Opposition%20party's%20during%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20given%20an%20option%20to%20pay%2020%20per%20cent%20in%202024%2C%20Rs%20135%20crore%20(was)%20recovered.%20Rs%201%2C700%20crore%20demand%20has%20been%20raised%20later.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20matter%20pertains%20to%20Rs%201%2C700%20subsequently%20raised.%20This%20whole%20matter%20can%20be%20fixed%20for%20post%20elections.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20any%20action%20till%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20the%20Centre%20is%20pausing%20the%20tax%20demand%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20are%20just%20saying%20that%20we%20will%20not%20take%20any%20action%20till%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20collected%20Rs%20135%20crore%20by%20attaching%20properties.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20a%20profit-making%20organisation%2C%20only%20a%20political%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20he%20has%20much%20to%20say%20on%20the%20merits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20issues%20arising%20in%20the%20appeals%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20adjudicated%20upon%20and%20that%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20on%20merits%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20reason%20to%20feel%20relieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20was%20in%20serious%20violation%20of%20tax%20laws%2C%20but%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20was%20not%20acting%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20warned%20that%20when%20the%20government%20changes%2C%20exemplary%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20no%20one%20dares%20to%20take%20such%20steps%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20government%20changes%2C%20action%20will%20definitely%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20have%20disrobed%20democracy.%20And%20such%20exemplary%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20that%20no%20one%20will%20dare%20to%20do%20all%20this%20again.%20This%20is%20my%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20alleged%20that%20efforts%20were%20being%20made%20to%20financially%20cripple%20the%20Congress%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20cowed%20down%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20leader%20Ajay%20Maken%20said%20the%20Congress%20was%20being%20selectively%20targeted.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20are%20saying%20is%20that%20there%20should%20be%20a%20level-playing%20field.%20This%20action%20was%20designed%20to%20choke%20the%20Congress%20financially%20and%20prevent%2C%20stop%2C%20delay%20and%20disable%20any%20election-related%20expenditure%20by%20the%20party%20on%20advertisements%2C%20travel%2C%20salaries%2C%20agencies%20etc.%20It%20is%20indeed%20appalling%20that%20the%20financial%20years%20assessed%20go%20back%20to%201993-94%2C%20when%20the%20late%20Sitaram%20Kesri%20was%20the%20party's%20treasurer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20orders%20are%20based%20on%20manufactured%20and%20planted%20diaries%20and%20so-called%20raids%20by%20the%20BJP's%20frontal%20organisation%20on%20third%20parties.%20Several%20of%20these%20raided%20third%20parties%20enjoy%20stay%20orders%20from%20courts%20based%20on%20vitiated%20search%20procedures%20by%20I-T%20department%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20alleged.%20Maken%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20same%20interim%20relief%20is%20not%20being%20granted%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711954500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fcp9nudu_congress-cwc-sonia-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-rahul-gandhi-sonia-rahul-kharge_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-take-steps-to-recover-dues-during-polls-income-tax-breather-for-congress-5350028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWon't%20Take%20Steps%20To%20Recover%20Dues%20During%20Polls%26quot%3B%3A%20Income%20Tax%20Breather%20For%20Congress%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-take-steps-to-recover-dues-during-polls-income-tax-breather-for-congress-5350028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Excise%20policy%20case%3A%20Kejriwal%20remanded%20in%20judicial%20custody%20till%20April%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711954490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1711091255-7141.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-policy-case-kejriwal-remanded-in-judicial-custody-till-april-15-124040100295_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20to%20reporters%20before%20entering%20court%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20doing(referring%20to%20his%20arrest)%20is%20not%20good%20for%20the%20country%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-policy-case-kejriwal-remanded-in-judicial-custody-till-april-15-124040100295_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-policy-case-kejriwal-remanded-in-judicial-custody-till-april-15-124040100295_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-policy-case-kejriwal-remanded-in-judicial-custody-till-april-15-124040100295_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CSK%20Coach%20Explains%20MS%20Dhoni's%20Batting%20Approach%20Against%20Delhi%20Capitals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20not%20many%20better%20than%20the%20great%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20game%20awareness%20and%20that%20reflected%20in%20his%20maiden%20outing%20with%20the%20bat%20this%20IPL%20season%2C%20said%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20head%20coach%20Stephen%20Fleming.%20The%20margin%20of%20defeat%20for%20CSK's%20first%20loss%20of%20the%20season%20would%20have%20been%20bigger%20than%2020%20runs%20if%20it%20was%20not%20for%20Dhoni's%20unbeaten%2037%20off%2016%20balls%20at%20number%20eight.%20Dhoni's%20cameo%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20included%20a%20thundering%20six%20over%20extra-cover%20before%20he%20unleashed%20a%20one-handed%20maximum%20over%20mid-wicket%20in%20the%2020th%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%2C%20who%20last%20played%20for%20India%20in%202019%2C%20had%20undergone%20a%20knee%20surgery%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20beautiful%20wasn't%20it%3F%20He%20has%20been%20playing%20incredibly%20well%20pre-season.%20He%20is%20coming%20back%20from%20quite%20a%20serious%20injury.%20His%20batting%20has%20been%20superb.%20it%20gave%20us%20a%20positive%20vibe%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20a%20tough%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20get%20within%2020%20(runs%20of%20the%20target)%20run%20rate%20wise%20is%20important%20and%20he%20knows%20that.%20The%20way%20he%20played%20was%20spectacular%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20New%20Zealand%20captain%20at%20the%20post%20match%20press%20conference%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20loss%20of%20the%20season%2C%20Fleming%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20result%20today%20is%20a%20fair%20reflection%20of%20the%20team's%20play%20tonight.%20We%20were%20a%20little%20bit%20off%20tonight%2C%20we%20were%20slow%20at%20start%20in%20the%20first%20six%20overs%20of%20each%20innings.%20We%20gave%20away%20too%20many%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20six%20when%20we%20bowled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20batted%2C%20they%20were%20very%20good%2C%20created%20pressure%20and%20used%20the%20conditions%20very%20well.%20The%20little%20cameos%20from%20David%20Warner%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%20pushed%20them%20to%20a%20very%20good%20score%20(191%2F5).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20waiting%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20perform%3A%20Khaleel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft-arm%20pacer%20Khaleel%20Ahmed's%20burst%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20put%20CSK%20on%20the%20backfoot%20from%20the%20outset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20waiting%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20perform%20for%20the%20team.%20When%20I%20started%2C%20I%20realised%20I%20was%20getting%20good%20swing%2C%20so%20I%20just%20backed%20it%20up%20and%20didn't%20allow%20the%20opposition%20any%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20play%2C%20the%20more%20you%20understand%20your%20game.%20The%20same%20happened%20with%20me%20as%20I%20have%20been%20playing%20continuously%20for%20six%20months%2C%20I%20got%20to%20understand%20my%20game%20plans%2C%20my%20body%20and%20managing%20to%20play%20in%20small%20niggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20all%20came%20due%20to%20the%20domestic%20season%2C%20it%20gave%20me%20good%20confidence%20before%20coming%20into%20the%20IPL%20and%20it's%20been%20a%20great%20feeling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711954080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcee5ab2o_stephen-fleming-bcci_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcsk-coach-stephen-fleming-explains-why-ms-dhoni-batting-approach-against-delhi-capitals-5350002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20margin%20of%20defeat%20for%20CSK's%20first%20loss%20of%20the