3E%26quot%3BOne%2C%20the%20most%20basic%20recurring%20(aspect)%20is%20the%20indifference%20shown%20by%20the%20then%20central%20government%20and%20the%20PMs%20about%20the%20territory%20of%20India.%20The%20fact%20is%20they%20simply%20did%20not%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BTo%20Pandit%20Nehru%2C%20this%20was%20a%20little%20island%2C%20it%20had%20no%20importance%2C%20and%20he%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20nuisance.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20sooner%20you%20give%20it%20away%2C%20the%20better.%20This%20view%20continued%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PM%20(Indira%20Gandhi)%20is%20said%20to%20have%20remarked%20in%20the%20AICC%20meeting%20that%20this%20is%20a%20little%20rock...so%2C%20this%20is%20not%20just%20one%20PM.%20This%20dismissive%20attitude%20was%20the%20historic%20Congress%20attitude%20towards%20Katchatheevu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20reminded%20of%20those%20days%20when%20Pandit%20Nehru%20called%20our%20northern%20boundary%20a%20place%20where%20not%20a%20blade%20of%20grass%20grew.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20that%20after%20this%20historic%20statement%20by%20PM%20Nehru%2C%20he%20never%20regained%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fishermen%20are%20still%20being%20detained%20today%2C%20boats%20are%20still%20being%20apprehended%20and%20the%20issue%20is%20still%20being%20raised%20in%20Parliament.%20It%20is%20being%20raised%20in%20Parliament%20by%20two%20parties%20who%20did%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20there%20was%20an%20arrest%2C%20how%20do%20you%20think%20they%20(fishermen)%20were%20released%3F%20It%20is%20very%20good%20to%20give%20statements%20from%20Chennai%2C%20but%20the%20people%20who%20do%20the%20work%20are%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20know%20not%20only%20who%20did%20it%20but%20also%20who%20hid%20it%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BDMK%20questions%20