Had%20Ovarian%20Cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20case%20of%20misdiagnosis%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20woman%20in%20the%20UK%20was%20told%20by%20doctors%20that%20she%20was%20pregnant%20when%20she%20had%20ovarian%20cancer.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9x6r5n78w7o%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Emma%20Colledge%20visited%20a%20doctor%20in%C2%A0February%202022%20after%C2%A0experiencing%20bloating%20and%20frequent%20toilet%20visits.%C2%A0She%20thought%20it%20was%20probably%20due%20to%20allergies%20or%20irritable%20bowel%20syndrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%C2%A0told%20her%20she%20had%20a%20bloated%20stomach%20because%20she%20was%20pregnant%2C%20but%20her%20pregnancy%20tests%20came%20back%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Colledge%20said%3A%20''I%20went%20to%20the%20doctors%20in%20May%20and%20they%20told%20me%20I%20was%20pregnant.%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20and%20the%20test%20confirmed%20that.%20I%20know%20people%20say%20'don't%20Google%20it'%2C%20but%20when%20I%20Googled%20my%20symptoms%20it%20always%20said%20that%20ovarian%20cancer%20is%20found%20in%20people%20mostly%20aged%2050%20and%20over.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Colledge%20was%20given%20an%20appointment%20for%20further%20investigations%2C%20but%20before%20she%20could%20go%20to%20it%2C%20the%20pain%20became%20intense.%C2%A0She%20then%20had%20an%20ultrasound%20which%20showed%20she%20had%20a%20cyst%20in%20her%20stomach.%20She%20was%20eventually%20diagnosed%20with%20ovarian%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Colledge%20said%2C%20''When%20I%20was%20first%20diagnosed%2C%20I%20was%20questioning%20whether%20I'd%20make%20it%20to%20my%2024th%20birthday%2C%20or%20if%20I'd%20die%20tomorrow.%20But%20I%20am%20very%20strong-willed.%20I'm%20stubborn%20and%20I%20told%20myself%20that%20this%20isn't%20my%20time%20to%20go%2C%20and%20I'm%20making%20sure%20of%20that.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20had%20spread%20to%20my%20stomach%20and%20the%20stomach%20lining.%20The%20cyst%20was%20so%20big%20that%20they%20couldn't%20see%20anything%20else%20because%20it%20had%20started%20crushing%20my%20kidneys.%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20too%20young%20to%20get%20ovarian%20cancer.%20It's%20not%20common.%20But%20it%20was%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20underwent%20a%20five-and-a-half-hour%20operation%20to%20remove%20the%20cyst%20and%20the%20ovary%20that%20was%20attached%20to%20it.%20She%20also%20had%20another%20surgery%20that%C2%A0took%20over%20nine%20hours%20and%20included%20a%20hysterectomy%2C%20and%20removal%20of%20her%20appendix%2C%20spleen%20and%20part%20of%20her%20bowel%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F03%2F31%2Fdoctors-told-woman-24-pregnant-cancerous-cyst-20562533%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20had%20six%20rounds%20of%20chemotherapy%20at%20the%20Teenage%20Cancer%20Trust%20unit%20at%20the%20Freeman%20Hospital%20in%20Newcastle.%20Her%20last%20chemotherapy%20treatment%20was%20in%202023%20and%20scans%20since%20then%20have%20shown%20no%20sign%20of%20cancer%20returning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Teenage%20Cancer%20Trust%20said%20ovarian%20cancer%20was%20getting%20more%20common%20in%20young%20people.%20''Knowing%20the%20signs%20of%20ovarian%20cancer%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20but%20remember%20that%20lots%20of%20conditions%20less%20serious%20than%20cancer%20can%20also%20cause%20these%20symptoms%2C''%20the%20trust%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%C2%A0Colledge%20is%20now%20using%20her%20experience%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20issue%20and%20asking%20young%20women%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20ovarian%20cancer%20symptoms.%20Symptoms%20included%20pain%20around%20the%20pelvis%20and%20tummy%2C%20bloating%20and%20struggling%20to%20eat%20because%20you%20feel%20full%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711950600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fta15380g_doctor_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-with-bloated-stomach-was-told-she-was-pregnant-she-actually-had-ovarian-cancer-5349743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20told%20her%20she%20had%20a%20bloated%20stomach%20because%20she%20was%20pregnant%2C%20but%20her%20pregnancy%20tests%20came%20back%20negative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-with-bloated-stomach-was-told-she-was-pregnant-she-actually-had-ovarian-cancer-5349743%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madgaon%20Express%20holds%20steady%20in%202nd%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711950277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108933716%2Cimgsize-83152.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fmadgaon-express-box-office-collection-kunal-kemmus-directorial-venture-earns-rs-3-5-crore-in-second-weekend%2Farticleshow%2F108933769.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108933769.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKunal%20Kemmu's%20directorial%20venture%2C%20'Madgaon%20Express'%2C%20earned%20Rs%203.5%20crore%20in%20its%20second%20weekend%2C%20totaling%20Rs%2017.09%20crore.%20The%20film%2C%20backed%20by%20Farhan%20Akhtar%20and%20Ritesh%20Sidhwani%2C%20offers%20Kunal's%20twist%20on%20a%20Goa%20trip%20gone%20wrong%2C%20starring%20Divyendu%20Sharma%2C%20Pratik%20Gandhi%2C%20Avinash%20Tiwary%2C%20and%20Nora%20Fatehi.%20It%20faces%20competition%20from%20'Crew'%2C%20which%20has%20amassed%20nearly%20