cknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20pacer%20Mayank%20Yadav%20made%20his%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20debut%20with%20a%20bang%2C%20troubling%20batters%20with%20his%20fiery%20pace%2C%20hitting%20the%20150%20kmph-plus%20mark%20consistently%20and%20bowling%20a%20game-changing%20spell%20to%20guide%20his%20team%20to%20a%2021-run%20win%20over%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20at%20Ekana%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%20His%20debut%20has%20earned%20him%20acclaim%20from%20some%20of%20the%20best%20bowlers%20to%20ever%20play%20the%20game%2C%20including%20pace%20greats%20like%20Brett%20Lee%20of%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa's%20Dale%20Steyn.%20Before%20the%20Saturday's%20IPL%20game%2C%20Mayank%20has%20played%20two%20first-class%20matches%2C%2017%20List-A%20games%20and%2011%20T20%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20represents%20Delhi%20at%20the%20domestic%20level%2C%20having%20made%20his%20List-A%20debut%20in%202021%20and%20his%20first-class%20debut%20in%202022.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20broadcasters%2C%20here%20are%20the%20bowling%20speeds%20per%20delivery%20(in%20kmph)%20of%20Mayank's%20unbelievable%20spell%20of%203%2F27%20in%2010%20overs%2C%20in%20which%20he%20dismissed%20Jonny%20Bairstow%2C%20Prabhsimran%20Singh%20and%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20to%20swing%20the%20tides%20in%20Lucknow's%20favour%20following%20a%20century%20partnership%20between%20Bairstow%20and%20skipper%20Shikhar%20Dhawan%20in%20a%20200-run%20chase.%20He%20took%20home%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1st%20over%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E147%2C%20146%2C%20150%2C%20141%2C%20149%2C%20147%20(in%20kmph)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2nd%20over%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E156%2C%20150%2C%20142%2C%20144%20(wicket)%2C%20153%2C%20149%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3rd%20over%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E152%2C%20150%2C%20147%20(wicket)%2C%20146%2C%20144%2C%20143%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4th%20over%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E153%2C%20154%2C%20149%2C%20142%20(wicket)%2C%20152%2C%20148%3C%2Fp%3E%