a%20younger%20brother%20than%20a%20colleague.%20We%20have%20stood%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20on%20significant%20issues%20and%20at%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20brotherhood%20and%20respect%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20shahid%20siddiqui%20(%40shahid_siddiqui)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshahid_siddiqui%2Fstatus%2F1774616418090442812%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%5Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20I%20resigned%20from%20the%20position%20of%20National%20Vice%20President%20of%20RLD%20%26amp%3B%20its%20membership.%20Me%20and%20my%20family%20stood%20up%20against%20Indira's%20Emergency%20%26amp%3B%20today%20can't%20silently%20watch%20undermining%20of%20all%20the%20institutions%20which%20have%20united%20%26amp%3B%20made%20India%20one%20of%20the%20great%20nations%20of%20the%20world.%20My%20regards%20%26amp%3B%20best%20wishes%20to%20%40jayantrld%20%26amp%3B%20other%20colleagues%20in%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Chaudhary%2C%20after%20months%20of%20speculation%2C%20joined%20the%20NDA%20after%20the%20centre%20conferred%20his%20late%20grandfather%20and%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20which%20eyes%20Western%20UP%20with%20optimism%2C%20to%20achieve%20its%20ambitious%20target%20of%20370%20seats%20on%20its%20own%2C%20despite%20facing%20setbacks%20in%20the%20last%20elections%2C%20wants%20to%20consolidate%20its%20base%20among%20the%20Jats%2C%20which%20are%20the%20RLD's%20core%20base%2C%20and%20place%20it%20ahead%20in%20at%20least%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jat%20community%20has%20significant%20influence%20in%20a%20dozen%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20around%2040%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20West%20UP.%20They%20are%20estimated%20to%20make%20up%20between%2010%20and%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20in%20some%2015%20districts%20but%20are%20socially%20dominant%2C%20vocal%2C%20and%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20build%20a%20political%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%2024%20out%20of%2027%20seats%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20dwindled%20to%2019%20in%202019%2C%20with%20all%20eight%20seats%20going%20to%20the%20SP-BSP%20combine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddiqui%2C%20however%2C%20wrote%20a%20separate%20post%20for%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20and%20hailed%20his%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20secularism%20and%20constitutional%20values%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRespected%20Jayantji%2C%20we%20have%20worked%20together%20for%206%20long%20years%20and%20have%20respect%20for%20each%20other.%20I%2C%20for%20one%2C%20look%20upon%20you%20more%20as%20a%20younger%20brother%20than%20a%20colleague.%20We%20have%20stood%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20on%20significant%20issues%20and%20at%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20brotherhood%20and%20respect%20among%20different%20communities.%20No%20one%20can%20doubt%20your%20commitment%20to%20secularism%20and%20the%20Constitutional%20values%20we%20both%20cherish.%20From%20the%20time%20of%20your%20late%20grandfather%2C%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Choudhary%20Charan%20Singhji%2C%20your%20late%20father%20Ajit%20Singhji%2C%20and%20yourself--all%20of%20you%2C%20as%20indeed%20the%20party%20you%20created%20have%20stood%20for%20these%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Siddiqui%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20RLD%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20puts%20him%20in%20a%20bind%20and%20a%20piquant%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20struggled%20long%20and%20hard%20in%20my%20mind%20and%20heart%20but%20find%20myself%20unable%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20an%20alliance%20headed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20your%20political%20compulsions%20and%20am%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20advise%20you%20otherwise.%20But%20speaking%20for%20myself%20I%20am%20constrained%20to%20withdraw%20myself%20from%20this%20ongoing%20campaign%2C%20as%20indeed%20from%20the%20RLD%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20RLD%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKindly%20accept%20my%20resignation.%20As%20always%20wishing%20you%20all%20the%20very%20best%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5CnLok%20Sabha%20polls%20will%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20phases%20beginning%20April%2019.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20sends%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20MPs%2C%2080%2C%20to%20Parliament%2C%20will%20vote%20in%20all%20seven%20phases.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20political%20dynamics%20shifting%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20spearheading%20a%20robust%20alliance%2C%20encompassing%20parties%20like%20RLD%2C%20SBSP%2C%20Apna%20Dal%20(S)%2C%20and%20Nishad%20party%20bolstering%20its%20position.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20while%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20aligns%20with%20the%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20Mayawati%20embarks%20on%20the%20electoral%20journey%20solo.%3Cbr%3E%5CnVoting%20for%20phases%20one%20and%20two%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2019%20and%20April%2026.%20Next%2C%20the%20state%20will%20once%20again%20poll%20in%20phases%20three%20and%20four%20on%20May%207%20and%20May%2013.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20electorate%20will%20also%20vote%20in%20phases%20five%2C%20six%20and%20seven%20on%20May%2020%2C%20May%2023%20and%20June%201%20respectively.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711948500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmd0lgb08_shahid-siddiqui_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fundermining-of-institutions-rld-vice-president-shahid-siddiqui-quits-party-after-bjp-tie-up-5349331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shahid%20Siddiqui%2C%20the%