said%20last%20week%20that%20his%20candidacy%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bspoiler%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20Biden%20and%20Trump.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20strategist%20James%20Carville%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20MSNBC%20interview%2C%20said%20that%20independent%20candidate%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.'s%20presidential%20campaign%20might%20be%20a%20drag%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%202024%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20observers%20say%20Kennedy%20Jr.'s%20campaign%20would%20harm%20Biden%2C%20the%20veteran%20Democratic%20strategist%20took%20the%20opposite%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20think%20Bobby%20Kennedy%20might%20hurt%20Trump%20more%20than%20he%20hurts%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20host%20Ari%20Melber%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20polling%20of%20three-way%20matchups%20between%20Biden%2C%20Trump%2C%20and%20Kennedy%20Jr.%2C%20the%20former%20president%20is%20often%20slightly%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20Jr.%2C%20an%20environmental%20lawyer%20who%20last%20week%20selected%20lawyer%20Nicole%20Shanahan%20as%20his%20vice%20presidential%20running%20mate%2C%20said%20recently%20that%20he%20intended%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bspoiler%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20arguing%20that%20he'd%20appeal%20to%20voters%20who%20wanted%20a%20break%20from%20the%20two%20major-party%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20campaign%20is%20a%20spoiler%20all%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20said%20during%20an%20event%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kennedy24.com%2Fkennedy_welcomes_nicole_shanahan_vice_president%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewelcoming%20Shanahan%20to%20the%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20spoiler%20for%20the%20war%20machine.%20It%20is%20a%20spoiler%20for%20Wall%20Street%2C%20Big%20Ag%2C%20Big%20Tech%2C%20and%20Big%20Pharma%2C%20the%20corporate%20media%2C%20and%20all%20of%20the%20corrupt%20politicians%20and%20corporations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20Jr.%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20late%20New%20York%20Sen.%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20is%20averaging%2012.3%25%20support%20in%20national%20polling%20in%20a%20three-way%20race%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realclearpolling.com%2Fpolls%2Fpresident%2Fgeneral%2F2024%2Ftrump-vs-biden-vs-kennedy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20RealClearPolling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20polling%20taken%20from%20late%20January%20through%20late%20March%2C%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20are%20each%20averaging%2040.7%25%20and%2035.3%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20a%20three-way%20contest%20with%20Kennedy%20Jr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20pure%20matchup%20between%20Biden%20and%20Trump%2C%20the%20former%20president%20is%20averaging%20a%20slim%201-point%20lead%20over%20the%20incumbent%20(46.5%25-45.5%25)%20in%20March%20polling%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realclearpolling.com%2Fpolls%2Fpresident%2Fgeneral%2F2024%2Ftrump-vs-biden%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20RealClearPolling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarville%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-carville-biden-2020-electoral-coalition-democrats-male-engagement-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20about%20cracks%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20electoral%20foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20presidential%20campaigns%20of%20Cornel%20West%20and%20Jill%20Stein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategist%20noted%20that%20a%20slice%20of%20Americans%20have%20a%20%26quot%3BJust%20F%20the%20whole%20thing%26quot%3B%20view%20of%20the%20election%20and%20stated%3A%20%26quot%3BBiden%20is%20not%20gonna%20get%20any%20of%20the%20'F%20it%20all'%20vote%2C%20OK%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20what%20worries%20me%20is%20Cornel%20West%20and%20Jill%20Stein%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20some%20of%20the%20'F%20it%20all'%20vote%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he