n%20in%20the%20royal%20town.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20unfortunately%2C%20most%20of%20the%20tourists%20would%20only%20visit%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20and%20not%20come%20to%20Rajpipla%2C%20even%20though%20the%20town%20is%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20drive%20from%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2038-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhanshyam%20tried%20different%20methods%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20guests%20visiting%20his%20hostel%20%E2%80%94%20from%20creating%20an%20Instagram%20page%20to%20regularly%20posting%20content%20to%20draw%20attention.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20nothing%20worked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20eight%20months%20back%2C%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Delhi-based%20startup%20%E2%80%98Volunteer%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20helped%20him%20expand%20his%20business.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20team%20helped%20us%20record%20good%20quality%20content%20using%20drones%20and%20captivating%20videos%20highlighting%20local%20culture%20and%20food.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20decorated%20the%20property%20using%20murals%20on%20walls%20and%20creative%20maps%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20boosted%20Ghanshyam%E2%80%99s%20followers%20from%20400%20to%20over%201%2C000%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20visitors%20visiting%20his%20hostel%3B%20thereby%20increasing%20his%20income%20by%2020%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20started%20finding%20us%20on%20social%20media.%20Now%2C%20we%20welcome%2060%20to%2070%20guests%20in%20a%20month%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%2020%20to%2030%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20rural%20residents%2C%20Ghanshyam%20could%20have%20moved%20to%20the%20city%20for%20better%20job%20opportunities%2C%20but%20he%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20village.%20And%20thanks%20to%20Volunteer%20Yatra%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20run%20a%20thriving%20business%20while%20being%20rooted%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Egot%20in%20touch%20with%20Aakash%20Maan%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Volunteer%20Yatra%2C%20to%20know%20how%20he%20is%20tapping%20into%20volunteer%20tourism%20to%20help%20small%20businesses%20flourish%20and%20prevent%20rural%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20travel%20as%20a%20tool%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%2C%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20possesses%20expertise%20in%20marketing%2C%20filmmaking%2C%20and%20photography.%20His%20passion%20for%20entrepreneurship%20ignited%20during%20his%20college%20years%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20venture%20into%20business.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20engineering%20college%20and%20establish%20his%20own%20production%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20while%20working%20on%20a%20film%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20I%20realised%20the%20potential%20harm%20that%20forces%20rural%20communities%20to%20migrate%20to%20cities%20for%20work%20leaving%20their%20homes%20behind.%20After%20the%20film%20was%20released%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20action-oriented%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Aakash%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20friend%20in%20Himachal%20that%20helped%20him%20realise%20his%20true%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20friend%20used%20to%20run%20a%20homestay%20but%20this%20business%20was%20adversely%20affected%20amid%20the%20lockdown.%20He%20was%20in%20extreme%20losses%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20money%20to%20arrange%20two%20square%20meals%20for%20his%20family.%20He%20asked%20for%20my%20help%20in%20marketing%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20two%20months%20to%20draw%20tourists%20to%20his%20homestay.%20In%20three%20months%2C%20he%20started%20earning%20up%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000%20a%20month.%20He%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20he%20offered%20me%20to%20visit%20him%20anytime%20and%20stay%20as%20long%20as%20I%20wanted.%20This%20gave%20me%20the%20idea%20to%20collaborate%20with%20similar%20small%20businesses%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20the%20support%20of%20skilled%20volunteers%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20will%20get%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20offbeat%20places%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20six%20months%20of%20research%2C%20Aakash%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Karunesh%20Maan%20and%20Rakshit%20Kumar%20launched%20Volunteer%20Yatra%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20win-win%20for%20volunteers%20and%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20platform%20works%2C%20Aakash%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20small%20businesses%20are%20dependent%20on%20travel%20agents%20to%20attract%20tourists.%20As%20they%20cannot%20afford%20skilled%20marketing%20experts%20and%20content%20creators%20to%20promote%20their%20works%2C%20we%20shortlisted%20volunteers%20to%20address%20this%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20developing%20the%20right%20marketing%20strategies%2C%20Aakash%20assigns%20volunteers%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%20to%20visit%20small%20business%20owners.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20their%20brief%20on-site%20travel%2C%20they%20assist%20them%20in%20promoting%20their%20work%20through%20content%20creation%2C%20graphic%20designing%2C%20optimising%20social%20media%2C%20creating%20murals%20on%20walls%2C%20connecting%20with%20right%20partners%2C%20and%20much%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20volunteers%20are%20freelancers%2C%20on%20sabbatical%2C%20or%20those%20working%20from%20home.%20This%20also%20enables%20them%20to%20embark%20on%20meaningful%20journeys%20while%20they%20save%20on%20accommodation%20and%20food%20expenses%20and%20contribute%20to%20community%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Aakash%20and%20his%20team%20have%20established%20an%20army%20of%202%2C000%20active%20volunteers%20who%20collaborate%20with%20hosts%20for%20a%20period%20of%20six%20months%20to%20one%20year.%20So%20far%2C%20these%20volunteers%20have%20assisted%20170%20hosts%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20hostels%2C%20homestays%2C%20and%20self-help%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20country%20in%20states%20like%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20their%20volunteers%2C%20Prem%20Suraj%20Tenkar%20moved%20to%20Rajpipla%20to%20assist%20Ghanshyam%20in%20content%20creation%20and%20optimise%20social%20media.%20It%20has%20been%20more%20than%2040%20days%20since%20he%20arrived%20in%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20to%20Rover%20Stay%20hostel%2C%20I%20was%20their%20only%20guest%20for%20the%20next%2015%20days.%20Using%20my%20cinematic%20and%20storytelling%20skills%2C%20I%20recorded%20unique%20content%20about%20the%20region%20to%20attract%20tourists%20to%20Ghanshyam%E2%80%99s%20hostel.%20We%20also%20decorated%20domes%20using%20wall%20murals.%20All%20of%20my%20reels%20have%20crossed%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20views%20on%20Instagram.%20We%20are%20now%20working%20on%20a%20YouTube%20series%20to%20further%20attract%20tourists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20business%20observed%20growth%20after%2025%20days%2C%20for%20Prem%2C%20this%20experience%20has%20been%20extremely%20enriching%20personally.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20working%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20for%20seven%20years%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20travel.%20As%20a%20solo%20traveller%2C%20budget%20is%20always%20a%20constraint.%20But%20volunteering%20not%20only%20helped%20me%20use%20my%20skills%20for%20community%20development%20but%20also%20to%20pursue%20my%20passion.%20It%20was%20extremely%20rewarding%20to%20explore%20Rajpipla%20on%20my%20bike%20and%20record%20its%20scenic%20beauty%20on%20my%20GoPro%20and%20drone.%20I%20have%20explored%20the%20place%20more%20than%20I%20was%20expecting%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20sustain%20the%20for-profit%20business%2C%20Aakash%20charges%20an%20annual%20fee%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20from%20volunteers.%20While%20he%20charges%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20month%20from%20revenue-generating%20businesses%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20take%20no%20fee%20from%20non-profits%20and%20low-income%20businesses%20such%20as%20Ghanshyam%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20often%20I%20am%20the%20last%20person%20to%20draw%20a%20salary%20or%20sometimes%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20paid%20for%20months.%20It%20is%20tough.%20But%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20grow%20stronger%20and%20keep%20going%20with%20every%20impactful%20project%20that%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20making%20a%20positive%20difference%20through%20volunteer%20tourism%2C%20Aakash%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CVolunteer%20Yatra%20is%20much%20more%20than%20a%20volunteering%20platform.%20We%2C%20as%20a%20team%2C%20have%20solved%20the%20organisational%20problems%20of%20our%20hosts%20in%20the%20most%20affordable%20way.%20One%20of%20our%20hosts%20could%20pay%20for%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20tuition%20fee%20as%20his%20business%20took%20off%20after%20connecting%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20experienced%20so%20many%20stories%20already%2C%20with%20many%20more%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Volunteer%20Yatra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711772851887%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346015%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi-based%20Aakash%20Maan%20co-founded%20%E2%80%98Volunteer%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20to%20establish%20volunteer%20tourism%20and%20help%20small%20businesses%20flourish%2C%20preventing%20rural%20migration.%20Currently%2C%20he%20has%20an%20army%20of%20around%202%2C000%20active%20volunteers%20helping%20put%20rural%20homestays%20on%20the%20tourism%20map.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Grandma%E2%80%99s%20Traditional%20Rasam%20Powder%20Recipe%20Gave%20Birth%20to%20a%20Brand%20Earning%20Rs%2016%20Cr%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20began%20with%20a%20chance%20conversation%20between%20M%20S%20Ravindra%2C%20his%20wife%20Nagaratna%20Ravindra%2C%20and%20their%20relative%20Malathi%20Sharma%20in%202009.%20Ravindra%20had%20recently%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20General%20Mills%20and%20taken%20to%20agriculture%20full-time%2C%20while%20Nagaratna%20and%20Malathi%20were%20working%20their%20full-time%20jobs%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335353%2Fharish-closepet-masterchef-india-father-cooking-school-lunchbox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20this%20conversation%2C%20Ravindra%20spoke%20of%20his%20travels%20around%20India%20while%20working%20for%20General%20Mills%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20missing%20his%20native%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20(from%20South-Western%20Karnataka)%20and%20expressing%20his%20desire%20to%20take%20this%20unique%20culinary%20tradition%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20fate%20would%20have%20it%2C%20my%20aunt%20(Malathi)%20and%20parents%20(Ravindra%20and%20Nagaratna)%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20recipe%20to%20make%20small%20batches%20in%20a%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20family%20and%20friends.%20This%20was%20their%20%E2%80%98aha%E2%80%99%20moment%2C%20and%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat%20Kaushik%2C%20director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Adukale%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20Adukale%20is%20a%20leading%20ready-to-cook%20(RTC)%20and%20ready-to-eat%20(RTE)%20brand%20that%20reflects%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdukale%20was%20born%20out%20of%20sheer%20love%20and%20passion%20to%20bring%20time-tested%20Sankethi%20recipes%20to%20the%20fore.%20We%20gained%20significant%20popularity%20through%20word-of-mouth%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20immense%20popularity%20and%20demand%20for%20homegrown%20recipes.%20We%20moved%20on%20to%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246450%2Flakshmi-raj-grated-coconut-fresh-n-easy-kerala-instant-food-products-women-entrepreneur-buy-online-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20powders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Egojjavalakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(prepared%20using%20thick%20beaten%20rice%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%2C%20jaggery%2C%20tamarind%2C%20salt%20and%20coconut)%2C%20and%20subsequently%20opened%20our%20flagship%20store%20in%20Malleshwaram%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20started%20as%20a%20chance%20encounter%20has%20now%20become%20a%20way%20of%20life%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Malathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founder%20of%20Adukale%2C%20a%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20brand%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-S