rong%3EBringing%20the%20magic%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20to%20the%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20inception%20%5Bof%20Adukale%5D%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20watch%20my%20parents%20and%20aunt%20bring%20in%20their%20entrepreneurial%20prowess%20and%20passion%20to%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20few%20years%20after%20establishing%20Adukale%2C%20demand%20for%20their%20products%20grew%20so%20extensively%20in%20Bengaluru%20through%20just%20word%20of%20mouth%20that%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20move%20away%20from%20their%20small%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20in%20Malathi%E2%80%99s%20home%20to%20a%203%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2030%20tonnes.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20venture%20shifted%20to%20an%20even%20larger%207%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20in%20South%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20100%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20capacity%20growing%20multi-fold%2C%20their%20processes%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change.%20One%20of%20the%20three%20founding%20partners%20of%20the%20business%20continued%20to%20supervise%20each%20stage%20of%20production%20to%20ensure%20product%20quality%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wane.%20What%20also%20helped%20was%20Bharat%20joining%20the%20business%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWitnessing%20great%20promise%20in%20the%20venture%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20profession%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20to%20join%20Adukale.%20As%20someone%20passionate%20about%20food%20and%20the%20culinary%20landscape%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20in%20my%20global%20experience%20and%20innovation%20to%20scale%20the%20brand%20and%20make%20strides%20in%20br