2%80%9CTheir%20chicken%20Afghani%20momos%20and%20paneer%3Cem%3E%20tandoori%20momos%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20some%20of%20the%20juiciest%20momos%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyou%20will%20ever%20have%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20to%20try%20these.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20well-known%20food%20blogger%20Karan%20Marwah%20said%20that%20the%20momos%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere%20take%20him%20back%20to%20his%20college%20days.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20invent%20it%2C%20Hunger%20Strike%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Etandoori%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20momo%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20actually%20my%20introduction%20to%20this%20Delhi%20twist%20of%20this%20classic%20dish.%20Momo%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Edone%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Etandoor%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20tossed%20in%20butter%2C%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20coriander%2C%20these%20momos%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20addictive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%C2%A0%20Dolma%20Aunty%20Momo%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20737px)%20100vw%2C%20737px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fmomo-competition-2.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dolma%20aunty%20momos%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fmomo-competition-2.jpg%20737w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fmomo-competition-2-300x158.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fmomo-competition-2-500x263.jpg%20500w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-247481%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20momos%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Delhi%2C%20how%20could%20we%20ever%20miss%20out%20on%20this%20iconic%20place.%20Serving%20Delhi%20since%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20Dolma%20Tersing%20aka%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22