%E2%80%9CEstimates%20based%20on%20a%20recent%20multi-centric%20study%20reveal%20a%20dementia%20prevalence%20rate%20of%207.4%25%20among%20those%20aged%2060%20years%20and%20above%2C%20translating%20to%20nearly%209%20lakh%20Indians%20currently%20living%20with%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20an%20estimated%2088%20lakh%20in%202016%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20dementia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20to%201.7%20crore%20by%202036.%20The%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Prevalence%20of%20dementia%20in%20India%3A%20National%20and%20State%20estimates%20from%20a%20nationwide%20study%E2%80%99%20was%20published%20in%20July%20this%20year%20%5B2023%5D%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAlzheimer%E2%80%99s%20and%20Dementia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20journal%20of%20the%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20Association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%20at%20Ivory%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20research%20estimates%20show%20that%20one%20person%20in%20India%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20every%2020%20seconds.%20Contributing%20factors%20such%20as%20loneliness%2C%20increased%20nuclear%20families%20and%20sedentary%20lifestyles%20have%20added%20to%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20research%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20reports%20show%20that%20cases%20have%20increased%20from%20an%20estimated%205.3%20million%20in%202020%20to%208.8%20million%20in%202023.%20Furthermore%2C%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2070%2C%20even%20with%20mild%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20face%20a%201%20in%203%20chance%20of%20progressing%20to%20dementia%20within%20five%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20heightened%20dialogue%20and%20action%20in%20neuro%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Issac%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20Ivory%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20insufficient%20attention%20and%20understanding%20of%20dementia%2C%20especially%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20symptom%20identification%20tools%20combined%20with%20scant%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20advice%20at%20the%20right%20time%20makes%20this%20a%20pressing%20problem%20for%20every%20Indian%20household%20with%20an%20ageing%20parent.%20Urban%20seniors%2C%20particularly%20those%20living%20alone%2C%20face%20challenges%20in%20monitoring%20their%20cognitive%20health%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20%5BCOVID-19%5D%20pandemic-induced%20isolation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20Ivory%2C%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Ivory%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20developing%20a%20pioneering%20platform%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cognitive%20wellness%20of%20seniors%20and%20cultivating%20healthy%20brain%20habits.%20We%20offer%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20interactive%20content%2C%20social%20games%2C%20neuroscience-backed%20assessments%2C%20and%20comprehensive%20wellness%20programmes%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20cognitive%20well-being%20and%20mitigating%20the%20risk%20of%20brain-related%20ailments%20such%20as%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20this%20point%2C%20however%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy.%20As%20Issac%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20met%2C%20there%20were%20few%20ready%20reckoners%20and%20research%20available%20for%20companies%20who%20are%20building%20in%20age-tech%2C%20particularly%20in%20India%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20take%20any%20existing%20learnings%20and%20apply%20them%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20seniors.%20That%20meant%20that%20we%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20multiple%20product%20concepts%20parallelly%20before%20zeroing%20down%20on%20what%20would%20find%20mass%20pain-point%20resonance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntrepren