0quiz%20competition%2C%20radio%20programs%2C%20and%20jingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20region%20has%20observed%20a%20significant%20decrease%20of%20about%2053.33%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20from%2030%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%202019-21%20to%2014%20in%202022.%20Similarly%2C%20a%2057.35%20percent%20reduction%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20area%20affected%20by%20forest%20fires%20%E2%80%94%20from%2037.05%20to%2015.8%20hectares%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20results%20of%20the%20community-driven%20approach%2C%20Pritam%20requests%20local%20people%20in%20the%20fire-prone%20regions%20to%20step%20up%20and%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ejal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(water)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejungle%20%3C%2Fem%3E(forest)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejameen%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land)%20belong%20to%20all%20of%20us%20as%20a%20community%2C%20so%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20step%20up%20to%20safeguard%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20and%20consciously%20increase%20our%20awareness%20against%20forest%20fires.%20In%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20bust%20myths%20among%20villagers%20and%20reduce%20extreme%20forest%20fire%20incidences%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pritam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20then%20you%20too%20can.%20This%20Forest%20Day%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20pledge%20to%20save%20our%20jungles!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fukhand-loses-highest-561-2-ha-green-cover-in-24hrs-to-fires-over-2k-ha