posing%20used%20cooking%20oil%20into%20biodiesel%20that%20can%20be%20then%20redirected%20towards%20multiple%20purposes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20love%20snacking%20on%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20sold%20by%20your%20local%20vendor%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20then%20the%20next%20time%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20check%20on%20the%20oil%20he%20is%20using.%20According%20to%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%2C%20food%20business%20operators%20are%20supposed%20to%20discard%20vegetable%20oils%20after%20three%20times%20of%20frying%20or%20when%20their%20total%20polar%20compound%20(TPC)%20levels%20reach%2025%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20shocking%20is%20that%20though%20India%20generates%20three%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20%E2%80%98used%20cooking%20oil%E2%80%99%2C%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20it%20goes%20toward%20biodiesel%20production.%20What%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20rest%3F%20This%20startup%20is%20encouraging%20food%20outlets%20to%20channel%20the%20%E2%80%9Cused%E2%80%9D%20oil%20to%20them%20to%20convert%20into%20biodiesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Tvaran%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%2030%20tonnes%20of%20used%20cooking%20oil%20per%20month%20have%20been%20collected%20from%20over%20250%20vendors%20in%20South%20India%20and%20recycled%20into%20biofuel.%20Kalyani%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Tvaran%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20introduced%20to%20The%20Chennai%20Angels%20(TCA)%2C%20from%20whom%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20equity%20funding%20of%20Rs%203%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuccess%20stories%20like%20these%20fulfil%20the%20intention%20with%20which%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20conceptualised%20Tvaran.%20Kalyani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20simply%20zoomed%20in%20on%20this%20particular%20strategy.%20The%20shared%20interest%20when%20it%20came%20to%20supporting%20women%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20space%20helped%20us%20scale%20this%20idea%20into%20one%20that%20has%20impacted%20so%20many%20startups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20cohort%20enabled%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20to%20witness%20how%20market%20partnerships%20and%20support%20in%20implementing%20GTM%20strategies%20helped%20women-led%20businesses%2C%20as%20we%20advance%2C%20they%20say%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20fortify%20this%20cause.%20With%20the%20guiding%20belief%20that%20inventions%20are%20critical%20to%20driving%20change%2C%20the%20broader%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20these%20inventions%20get%20adopted%20while%20making%20communities%20resilient%